    <p>The week­end be­fore Christ­mas saw peo­ple out and about do­ing their last-minute shop­ping.</p>
    <p>While peo­ple were masked up, many malls and shops were crowded, checks by The Straits Times found. Re­tail­ers re­ported brisk sales amid the in­creased foot­fall while safe dis­tanc­ing of­fi­cers were on the ground to re­mind shop­pers to ob­serve the rules.</p>


